org.apache.james.api.imap.imap4rev1
Interface Imap4Rev1MessageFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseImap4Rev1MessageFactory
public interface Imap4Rev1MessageFactory

Creates messages. Implementations may support message pooling but this is not required.
